{"tid":2357568,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁頌恆被高等法院頒令破產","createTime":"2021-01-07T13:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T07:32:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4a64593a23f540a8abc8c63d4079a639f0151288","tid":2357568,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:34:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20210106193643\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20210106193643&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z3wORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=0cbed9fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20210106193643</a><br />\n<br />\n6/1/2021 19:36<br />\n        前青年新政立法會議員梁頌恆, 被高等法院正式頒令破產.<br />\n<br />\n        梁頌恆及前青年新政成員游蕙禎, 在2016年因為宣誓風波, 被褫奪立法會議員資格, 之後被立法會行管會追討已支付的議員薪酬津貼, 合共186萬元, 其中梁頌恆欠約93萬元.<br />\n<br />\n        梁頌恆去年11月到美國尋求政治庇護, 早前公開表示不會回港, 高等法院在梁頌恆缺席情況下, 接納行管會的破產呈請, 即時頒下對梁頌恆的破產令."},{"pid":"26d4e9d46fec0bddde3e99157be1a48b0bea4f04","tid":2357568,"uid":82938,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:35:11.000Z","msg":"應該攞埋d錢走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"c31b0647ee14e07633a4a442b1ba2e3ff6b58813","tid":2357568,"uid":389,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"26d4e9d46fec0bddde3e99157be1a48b0bea4f04","tid":2357568,"uid":82938,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:35:11.000Z","msg":"應該攞埋d錢走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"啲錢咪係個Office既裝修同電器<br />\n立會唔接受渣屌你老味"},{"pid":"60730ebb14aa504c227202e439b71a72e97abb4a","tid":2357568,"uid":199771,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:47:04.000Z","msg":"破產令是否包括<br />\n誠